{"tid":1134990,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"咩叫唔成熟（絲打請入）","createTime":"2019-05-02T04:46:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-02T06:59:18.000Z","uid":172031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5dbc2f2246cedc90e2c82b61e4322bf4afd47773","tid":1134990,"uid":172031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T04:46:14.000Z","msg":"其實我係隔離都開佐post ，但見一眾巴打講既唔成熟都離唔開「錢」同「喜歡既感覺」。<br />\n<br />\n咩叫成熟 （巴打入）<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1134824\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1134824</a><br />\n<br />\n所以想請問下絲打們，你地撫心自問，女人眼中既唔成熟，究竟係被濫用既詞語，定真係男方有野唔成熟？"},{"pid":"34e0d94dbf9480a05cc1cd01ecc8e3d8e732e598","tid":1134990,"uid":199162,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T04:55:58.000Z","msg":"自古以嚟 女人都係用關係嚟攞虛榮感<br />\n所以條仔做唔到個有地位嘅人 自己冇得打飛機 咪話佢唔成熟"},{"pid":"6becb03bc7f12800cbd3c3a1955806150baad5c7","tid":1134990,"uid":211461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T05:02:22.000Z","msg":"成唔成熟 好主觀<br />\n不如你問成熟有無客觀標準好過"},{"pid":"08991ac74507133b3d3ea37c1dec01f36b4ad323","tid":1134990,"uid":148385,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T05:03:02.000Z","msg":"1）諗野偏激非黑即白，將連登吹棒個套價值觀（例如仇女）帶到現實之中<br />\n2）對未來無打算<br />\n3）經常埋怨"},{"pid":"606f8720e10ed5874b41a69750e9d9ae11df123b","tid":1134990,"uid":181581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T05:09:35.000Z","msg":"事業有成嘅咪係成熟囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"001bb43414cf39034d6cdc2a97b1fef835a40038","tid":1134990,"uid":171310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T05:18:45.000Z","msg":"冇錢冇事業"},{"pid":"dce3746f99d81bac36720147df67db71cb0de36d","tid":1134990,"uid":157198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T06:37:55.000Z","msg":"處理事情既手法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n會考慮到所有人既感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n<br />\n利申唔成熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0134be8361b8a2e38cb7d0ef3386d6d68a85eb31","tid":1134990,"uid":76609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T06:40:08.000Z","msg":"咁嘅野都要開 post 問咪唔成熟"},{"pid":"10fb19ff7745cdcc9db63ed0f780151001d8dde8","tid":1134990,"uid":193476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T06:59:18.000Z","msg":"成唔成熟，係由生活穩定性同社會地位決定。<br />\n<br />\n一個住公屋既廚房仔，份糧僅僅夠養家，就算日日放工番屋企睇書自我增值，都係唔成熟既行為。<br />\n<br />\n另一個有屋企人比首期，日日放工返屋企打機，只要夠錢供樓，一年去四次旅行，呢啲就叫成熟。"}]}